I"<p>So the point of this whole holiday was to go visit Italy with dad and meet the relatives and I have to say I’m really glad I made it over. The 3-and-a-bit days I spent there was awesome.</p>

<p>The flight from London to Venice was ok, but the <a href="http://img.photobucket.com/albums/v236/mikezero/europe%202010/IMG_1965.jpg">view of the alps</a> as we flew over was incredible. I really have to get back to Switzerland sometime soon…</p>

<div style="width: 490px" class="wp-caption aligncenter">
  <a href="http://img.photobucket.com/albums/v236/mikezero/europe%202010/IMG_1966.jpg"><img class=" " title="farmhouses" src="http://img.photobucket.com/albums/v236/mikezero/europe%202010/IMG_1966.jpg" alt="" width="480" height="360" /></a>
  
