    Farm houses in Italian countryside
  </p>
</div>

<p>Everything is really making a lot more sense in my head now, one of the first things we did was went to Piran, where nonna came from. It’s a small coastal village which is now a part of Slovenia. The weather turned out great and we ended up spending almost all day there.</p>

<p>Obligatory terrible humour photo:</p>

<div style="width: 490px" class="wp-caption aligncenter">
  <a href="http://img.photobucket.com/albums/v236/mikezero/europe%202010/IMG_1975.jpg"><img class=" " title="poser bus" src="http://img.photobucket.com/albums/v236/mikezero/europe%202010/IMG_1975.jpg" alt="" width="480" height="360" /></a>
  
  <p class="wp-caption-text">
    All aboard the poser bus
